{"tid":226744,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"（收負皮）做男人如果無定力係大陸多數都會沉倫","createTime":"2017-05-02T17:03:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-13T18:22:08.000Z","uid":60338,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b26e3250bbdbb193b64c13e07076aa1e49f6f81b","tid":226744,"uid":60338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T17:03:08.000Z","msg":"的士陳就係一個好好既例子<br />\n各位只要平時工作或某D因素要關注下大陸D新聞<br />\n的士陳係大陸紅到你想像唔到<br />\n而佢紅既唔係佢才華。而只係佢有商業價值<br />\n我懷疑佢已經比人吹棒到真係相信自己真係唱歌好掂。拍戲好有演技。係大陸真係好容易會比誘惑掩蓋左當初既自己<br />\n<br />\n如果鄭伊健肯上去發展。我相信佢而加有錢到豬頭咁。前提佢要臉皮厚到好似的士陳咁。當然我地可以話佢。大陸有人賞識佢。唔通返黎香港做過街老鼠咩。但係我見到佢D活動好似完全係覺得自己好有才華盡現既表情"},{"pid":"320486006efc6828db90fbe188e6b0be9d1ba861","tid":226744,"uid":1713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T17:05:08.000Z","msg":"E 麵肯上去發展 黑社會大佬都有得做"},{"pid":"bf28efc8da853ebaa6f60b9bb25c82a7f417fc67","tid":226744,"uid":111889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T17:23:35.000Z","msg":"有關注大陸綜藝同娛樂新聞，有時會見到陳生，不過佢其實冇我地諗到咁紅，大陸四大當紅小生其實冇佢份，最多可以叫準一線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aa0f18cfe0a740a2aa422513cd1643284b06ffd","tid":226744,"uid":60338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T17:43:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有關注大陸綜藝同娛樂新聞，有時會見到陳生，不過佢其實冇我地諗到咁紅，大陸四大當紅小生其實冇佢份，最多可以叫準一線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我又無點睇綜藝。即係見到佢D劇同好似有巡迴演唱會好有曝光率？"},{"pid":"2cb879ffbcfff6157505a3aaed7f5b7bb666ea40","tid":226744,"uid":29676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T18:01:16.000Z","msg":"但佢點解有商業價值？"},{"pid":"615fe07c6208d2344ea5b8709893e69405d843b0","tid":226744,"uid":60338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T00:24:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但佢點解有商業價值？</blockquote><br />\n係大陸。只要唱歌唔係公牛聲。個樣唔係太差。基本有人棒一棒都紅透半邊天"},{"pid":"e5482676f464e2600efbde1c13921993e0754c12","tid":226744,"uid":14274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T03:03:10.000Z","msg":"謝霆鋒"},{"pid":"ee9d28ba528d9477ae5acef7391bf0af0c56d887","tid":226744,"uid":36600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T03:05:17.000Z","msg":"物以類聚，你們懂的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcae624271f3949d565110fb20473579593fe11e","tid":226744,"uid":36600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T03:06:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>謝霆鋒</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T52jcL3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT52jcL3.jpg&h=3212d3bb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/77462m4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F77462m4.jpg&h=f6f2548e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Drpz4NE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDrpz4NE.jpg&h=f9f1b820&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ec40ed6440e4cf4a0e8baab77fd6473fe81da4e0","tid":226744,"uid":111889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T17:54:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有關注大陸綜藝同娛樂新聞，有時會見到陳生，不過佢其實冇我地諗到咁紅，大陸四大當紅小生其實冇佢份，最多可以叫準一線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我又無點睇綜藝。即係見到佢D劇同好似有巡迴演唱會好有曝光率？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可以買架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大陸d做假文化真係周圍到有<br />\nd明星會喺d新聞網到買新聞做宣傳，百度search可以有上百條一模一樣新聞喺唔同平台出<br />\n陳生之前仲比微博官方點名話佢買微博讚好太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大陸娛圈仲有好多好痴線嘅文化，比如會計一樣叫番位嘅嘢，即係片尾邊個個名行先，就叫一番，所有收視成績都係一番嗰個人嘅成績<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"664e17f62a030c86